---
import ProjectLayout from "../../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout
    title="Desportos Náuticos de Alvor"
    category="E-Commerce & Merch"
    client="Desportos Náuticos"
    year="2024"
    description="Online booking system and inventory management for the largest nautical sports school in the Algarve."
    heroImage="/images/crm-macbook.png"
    lang="en"
    metrics={[
        { label: "Online Bookings", value: "+300%" },
        { label: "Operational Efficiency", value: "+80%" },
        { label: "Digital Payments", value: "100%" },
    ]}
>
    <div class="container project-content-grid">
        <div class="project-text-block" data-reveal>
            <h2>The Challenge</h2>
            <p>
                Desportos Náuticos de Alvor, the leader in nautical experiences
                in the Algarve, faced the challenge of managing hundreds of
                manual bookings daily. The lack of a centralized system resulted
                in scheduling errors and lost direct sales opportunities.
            </p>
            <p>
                The goal was to create a robust platform that allowed customers
                to book their experience in seconds, ensuring secure payment and
                immediate confirmation.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="project-media project-media-right"
            data-reveal
            class="reveal-delay-1"
        >
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544551763-46a013bb70d5?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000"
                alt="Luxury boat in Alvor"
                class="rounded-xl glass-panel p-2"
            />
        </div>

        <div class="project-media project-media-left mt-16" data-reveal>
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534440058864-4dccf1423cf9?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000"
                alt="Watersports equipment"
                class="rounded-xl glass-panel p-2"
            />
        </div>

        <div
            class="project-text-block mt-16"
            data-reveal
            class="reveal-delay-1"
        >
            <h2>The Solution</h2>
            <p>
                We developed a <strong>Service E-commerce</strong> focused on conversion.
                The new portal integrates a dynamic availability calendar, payment
                gateways (Stripe/Multibanco), and a complete control panel for the
                Desportos Náuticos team.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>3-step booking with dynamic time selection.</li>
                <li>
                    Mobile-first layout for "on-the-go" bookings at the beach.
                </li>
                <li>Automated confirmation emails and SMS reminders.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="project-full-media mt-24" data-reveal>
            <video
                autoplay
                loop
                muted
                playsinline
                class="rounded-2xl glass-panel w-full"
                style="padding: 0.5rem;"
            >
                <source
                    src="https://player.vimeo.com/external/498216173.sd.mp4?s=d0fb5b6e22f87a3cb1d4fbeb7f12ac26ddafb5fb&profile_id=165&oauth2_token_id=57447761"
                    type="video/mp4"
                />
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CRM Section -->
    <div class="crm-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="crm-header" data-reveal>
                <span class="crm-label">CRM & Backoffice</span>
                <h2>Internal Management System</h2>
                <p class="crm-intro">
                    Beyond the public booking portal, we built a complete backoffice from scratch using artificial intelligence — a custom CRM that centralises all of Desportos Náuticos de Alvor's operations in a single platform.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="crm-features" data-reveal>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Activity Control</h4>
                        <p>Real-time visual timeline for all school assets — jet-skis, wave runners, kayaks and towables. Session logging with payment tracking, partner attribution and offline sync queue.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Customer CRM</h4>
                        <p>Unified profiles that cross-reference bookings, concession visits and spending history by phone number. Automatic recurring customer detection with name suggestion and visit count.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Beach Concession Management</h4>
                        <p>Daily sunbed and umbrella control with a 14-day occupancy grid. Automatic Excel and PDF report exports with revenue breakdown by occupancy type.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Dashboards & Statistics</h4>
                        <p>Total and projected revenue, cancellation rate, activities by hour, new vs returning customers, and payment method breakdown — all in real time with auto-polling every 30 seconds.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Team Management</h4>
                        <p>Time-bank with GPS clock-in/out, per-staff schedules, shift swap system with notifications, and a sticky shift bar for quick clock-in/out from any page.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="crm-feature">
                    <div class="crm-feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2-2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Email Automation</h4>
                        <p>5 configurable templates — booking confirmation with QR code, concession reservation, review follow-up, shift swap and daily report. Preview, send history and per-type enable/disable toggles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="crm-mockups" data-reveal>
                <div class="crm-mockup-main">
                    <img src="/images/crm-macbook.png" alt="DNA CRM Dashboard — Admin panel" />
                </div>
                <div class="crm-mockup-side">
                    <img src="/images/crm-ipad.png" alt="DNA CRM — Activity Control on tablet" />
                    <img src="/images/crm-iphone.png" alt="DNA — Mobile availability portal" />
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</ProjectLayout>

<style>
    .project-content-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .project-text-block {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-text-block h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .project-text-block h2::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 0;
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        background: #38bdf8;
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .project-text-block p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }

    .project-text-block ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .project-text-block li {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .project-text-block li::before {
        content: "→";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #38bdf8;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .project-media img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.8s ease;
    }

    .project-media:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    .project-full-media {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .project-content-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .project-media-left {
            order: -1;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    }

    /* ── CRM SECTION ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .crm-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.03) 50%, transparent 100%);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .crm-header {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .crm-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        color: #22d3ee;
        background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
        padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .crm-header h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .crm-intro {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    }

    .crm-features {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .crm-feature {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .crm-feature-icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.18);
        border-radius: 10px;
        color: #22d3ee;
        margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .crm-feature h4 {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .crm-feature p {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    }

    .crm-mockups {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .crm-mockup-main img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: block;
    }

    .crm-mockup-side {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .crm-mockup-side img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: block;
    }

    .crm-built-with {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .built-tag {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .built-tag:last-child {
        background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
        border-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
        color: #22d3ee;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .crm-features {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .crm-features {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .crm-mockups {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .crm-mockup-side {
            flex-direction: row;
        }
    }
</style>
